promptResultCard.createPromptDescription.__value__: Open "Edit Prompt" and write your prompt or paste sections of other prompts.

promptResultCard.fillFormGenerateContent.__value__: Begin by filling out the prompt template inputs using natural language. Once you filled in the prompt template, select the "Generate" button.
Fill the Form and Generate Content

promptResultCard.generateContentDescript.__value__: If you've created input fields fill them in and select "Generate". Adobe's generative AI will process your input and generate unique content based on your specifications.

promptResultCard.refineContentDescriptio.__value__: After content is generated if you want to refine it further, update the prompt and / or input fields. Once you are happy with the content leverage in your AEM authoring experience.

promptResultCard.savePromptDescription.__value__: If you want to reuse the prompt created select "Save".  This allows you to store the prompt for future use. You can save it at the user or organization level.
